# PII patterns to block from commits.
# One regex per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# This file is tracked in git so all contributors know what's blocked.
# The pre-commit hook scans staged file contents against these patterns.

# Real names
alexander\.dueck
Alexander Dueck
alexd(?!eterminist)

# Email addresses (specific)
alex\.dueck123@
lex\.dueck@
@uvic\.ca

# Usernames / handles
flaplexalender
alexander123987

# Location identifiers
Victoria,?\s*BC
Victoria,?\s*British Columbia

# Hardcoded personal paths
C:\\Users\\Alexander
C:\\Users\\alexd
C:/Users/Alexander
C:/Users/alexd

# Proprietary mechanism details (do not expose in public repo)
X-Initiator
(?<!\d)0 premium
zero.premium
billing.*trick
